Dialogue: 1,0:01:22.15,0:01:27.65,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fscx80\fscy80}That is too late　そんな手じゃもう追いつけない
Dialogue: 1,0:01:27.65,0:01:29.65,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fscx80\fscy80}That is to say…
Dialogue: 1,0:01:29.65,0:01:32.57,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fscx80\fscy80}誰にももう追いつけない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.15,0:01:27.65,OP_CH,,0,0,80,,{\an8\fscx80\fscy80}为时已晚 凭借这一手是追不上我的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.65,0:01:29.65,OP_CH,,0,0,80,,{\an8\fscx80\fscy80}一切都在证明…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.65,0:01:32.57,OP_CH,,0,0,80,,{\an8\fscx80\fscy80}任谁都无法追赶上我
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,ED“Darling in the Night”
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.66,0:21:43.75,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur4}明けない夜なんてないっていうけれど
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.75,0:21:47.95,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur4}明けなくていいと　そう思ってた
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.55,0:21:50.88,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur4}隠したい傷跡だって
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.16,0:21:53.71,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur4}忘れたい記憶もみんな
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.02,0:21:58.61,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur4}太陽は全部照らし出すから
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.78,0:22:01.48,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur4}流星をさがし
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.21,0:22:04.00,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur4}彷徨ってたんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.85,0:22:11.84,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur4}あなたと出会う時まで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.30,0:22:18.85,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur4}空に瞬くあの星が
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.85,0:22:24.25,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur4}繋いだ希望の道の先へ行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.25,0:22:29.07,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur4}もう迷わずに進める
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.07,0:22:35.45,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur4}暗い夜を超える祈りを追いかけてく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.45,0:22:39.74,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur4}たとえまだ届かなくたって
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.55,0:22:43.90,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur4}伝えたいから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.90,0:22:45.22,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur4}「ありがとう」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.66,0:21:43.75,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur4}都说太阳总会升起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.75,0:21:47.95,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur4}但不升起也挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.55,0:21:50.88,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur4}想隐藏的伤痕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.16,0:21:53.71,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur4}想忘却的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.02,0:21:58.61,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur4}会被太阳照得一清二楚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.78,0:22:01.48,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur4}寻找着流星
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.21,0:22:04.00,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur4}独自彷徨着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.85,0:22:11.84,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur4}直到与你相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.30,0:22:18.85,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur4}在天空闪烁的那颗星
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.85,0:22:24.25,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur4}照亮了希望之路
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.25,0:22:29.07,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur4}不再迷茫 径直向前
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.07,0:22:35.45,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur4}跨过漆黑的夜晚 追随着祈愿
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.45,0:22:39.74,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur4}即使还传达不到
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.55,0:22:43.90,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur4}也想说一声
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.90,0:22:45.22,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur4}「谢谢」
